          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">When there is ambiguity as to which elements to select the <text styleclass="Interface">Select Elements dialog-box</text> opens.</para>
          <para styleclass="Interface">&lt;&lt;&lt; Select-Elements dialog-box</para>
