          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">Why not <text styleclass="Element-Header">Line3</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> and </text><text styleclass="Element-Header">CAD-Line</text> ? </para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-IT2"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">There is a </text><text styleclass="Element">Slide-Joint</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> between these two(2) </text><text styleclass="Element">CAD-Lines</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> already.</text></para>
